data.description: Charming 3/2 home with no HOA! This single family home is conveniently located in the heart of Winter Haven. It sits on an oversized lot with a shed for additional storage. The home has also been recently updated with fresh exterior paint, new windows, A/C, and insulation throughout the attic. Make this home yours today! Call for a private showing!
